{"tid":155782,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"連登EDM撚入","createTime":"2017-03-14T09:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T08:48:17.000Z","uid":73103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b214370132a7d80c980b42fc3a66f49d6e06b8","tid":155782,"uid":73103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打開po講edm<br />\n忍唔住都想講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nElectronic dance music=Edm<br />\n<br />\nedm係10年前大家一定唔係好留意，先唔講以前嘅disco music，淨係講dj電音<br />\n<br />\n10年前最hit會聽下r&amp;b，rap<br />\n<br />\n6,7年前最hit會聽lady gaga(poker face),Katy Perry(firework), Adele(Rolling in the deep),Taylor Swift等等<br />\n<br />\n甚至幾年前hit到爆嘅counting star, maroon5，pitbull(timber)等等<br />\n<br />\n到近年edm可以話佔據左樂壇主要地位<br />\n<br />\nedm係近5年發展迅速，Calvin Harris, Hardwell, avicii等等dj上位，出一場show都幾十萬美金<br />\n<br />\n入正題，The chainsmoker同coldplay最近出左隻新歌，見到d人不停吹捧同話好好聽，睇完都覺得嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> coldplay最hit個時嘅yellow, fix you, the scientist個d歌同dj電音夾咩?????我最多接受到coldplay作完歌比人remix，而唔係feature,feature左基本上coldplay呢隊band除左主音其餘可以收皮<br />\n<br />\n咁講唔係想話踩首歌難聽，唔係踩the chainsmoker，我由the chainsmoker出rose個首歌已經開始留意，而家佢紅左都合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想表達嘅係而家係咪一定要edm先會紅？好似the weekend嘅歌，勁多autotune, maroon5兩首新歌(don't wanna know,cold),全部都係edm<br />\n<br />\nEdm唔係唔好聽，因為變化多，易洗腦，聽得多係唔會悶，但係會好俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我第一個聽嘅dj係Calvin Harris,佢首summer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後開始聽hardwell, Steve aoki, Martin garrix, alesso等等，雖然過左咁耐但係仲保持到質素係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係而家樂壇就有粗製濫造嘅感覺，究竟係而家嘅歌手乾塘定係d聽眾質素下降？<br />\n<br />\n以前聽嘅pop music, country song, r&amp;b好似已經紅唔起，一式一樣嘅歌只要加d remix就反而紅到爆，就好似d泡菜垃圾食物加d芝士就令到d港女流唒水爭住食，我唔想之後見到dj會同Adele或者john legend合作，billboard top100都係edm<br />\n<br />\n唔知巴絲點睇，有錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMy top5 dj(純屬個人喜好)<br />\n<br />\n1.Calvin Harris<br />\n2.Robin Schulz<br />\n3.avicii<br />\n4.Martin garrix<br />\n5.G eazy<br />\n<br />\n太多dj, zedd,skrillex,alesso個d都不錯<br />\n<br />\n仲有avicii久休復出令人期待，tomorrowland亦都就快開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw小弟開左個日經音樂推介po,巴絲們可以得閒睇下"},{"pid":"1a47c1d06bc7c09d8bf4fc6d9033ef419af8a561","tid":155782,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"Pitbull都算學edm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7986e38b8f9e47ab0fdee8cd33331dbd638b9698","tid":155782,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pitbull都算EDM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"71a142c9dba674165aa8c7e648636a6c8ae34b12","tid":155782,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"東京熱隻歌<br />\n你都冇講<br />\n好打有限"},{"pid":"7d66203ff27f970b5f797c62b908f963a5c6fa62","tid":155782,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"Kshmr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n青smokers首closer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw roses個album係首選 佢出咁耐 我聽左咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5acae257ac70747dec2b7f5415e0b606a143763","tid":155782,"uid":12831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kshmr<img src=\"/asse